                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-141-off773 t18270712-141-cd774"></join>, 1 pair of spectacles, value 2s., and 1 hat, value 3s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270712-141-victim784" type="victimName">
                        Jonathan 
                        Bolton
                     <interp inst="t18270712-141-victim784" type="surname" value="Bolton"></interp>
