                     <interp inst="t18270712-141-person787" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I and Palmer apprehended the prisoners.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>MILTON'S Defence. The prosecutor came and took the spectacles out of my pocket - I had just found them in the grass - a lady saw me find them.</p>
               <p>MILTON - <rs id="t18270712-141-verdict776" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270712-141-verdict776" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 23.</p>
